OL,3,CCandidate to be next first minister
OL,4,Csays public 'profile' isn't everything
OL,6,FThe race is underway to become the
OL,7,Fnext leader of the Welsh Labour Party
OL,8,Fand as a result, the next First
OL,9,FMinister of Wales. Two candidates are
OL,10,Fvying for the top role but what makes
OL,11,Fthem different and what would each of
OL,12,Fthem do if they're successful?
OL,14,FIt is Welsh Labour members who will
OL,15,Fvote for who they want to be their
OL,16,Fnext leader but whoever wins will make
OL,17,Fdecisions that affect the entire
OL,18,Fcountry.
