OL,3,CCandidate to be next first minister
OL,4,Csays public 'profile' isn't everything
OL,6,FJeremy Miles MS, the Education
OL,7,FMinister, is one of those in the
OL,8,Frunning to become first minister. ITV
OL,9,FWales' Political Editor Adrian Masters
OL,10,Fsat down with him for a special
OL,11,Finterview to ask the question 'Who
OL,12,FWants to be the Next First Minister'?
OL,14,FIn a recent poll for ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,15,F3% of people asked thought Jeremy
OL,16,FMiles should be the next leader of the
OL,17,FWelsh Government, that is compared to
OL,18,F72% who did not know who should be the
OL,19,Fnext first minister.
