OL,3,CCandidate to be next first minister
OL,4,Csays public 'profile' isn't everything
OL,6,F11% thought Mr Miles' rival for the
OL,7,Fjob, Vaughan Gething MS, should be the
OL,8,Fnext leader of the party.
OL,10,FMr Miles said it is about more than
OL,11,Fjust a public "profile" when it comes
OL,12,Fto the right person for the job.
OL,14,FHe said: "I think what party members
OL,15,Fwho are going to be casting their
OL,16,Fvotes are looking for is a leader with
OL,17,Fvision, values and a clear sense of
OL,18,Fdirection for the years ahead.
