OL,3,CCandidate to be next first minister
OL,4,Csays public 'profile' isn't everything
OL,6,F"Profile is one thing, it's important
OL,7,Fbut it absolutely is not the thing
OL,8,Fthat most people will be voting for
OL,9,Fand that's a good thing."
OL,11,FAs Education Minister since 2021,
OL,12,FJeremy Miles has been responsible for
OL,13,Fdriving the Welsh Government's
OL,14,Feducation policies and strategies.
OL,16,FIn December 2023, the Programme for
OL,17,FInternational Student Assessment
OL,18,F(PISA) showed
OL,20,F"We know that Covid had a bad effect
OL,21,Fon scores everywhere," he explained.
