OL,3,CCandidate to be next first minister
OL,4,Csays public 'profile' isn't everything
OL,6,F"But I've had a plan since I became
OL,7,F(Education) Minister to focus on
OL,8,Fliteracy and numeracy and that's
OL,9,Fhappening - it just isn't happening in
OL,10,Ftime for these results."
OL,12,FWhen challenged on the point that PISA
OL,13,Fscores were also poor before the
OL,14,Fpandemic, Mr Miles said "results were
OL,15,Fgoing in a positive direction before
OL,16,FCovid" and he is "absolutely confident
OL,17,Fthey will go in the right direction
OL,18,Fagain".
