OL,3,CCandidate to be next first minister
OL,4,Csays public 'profile' isn't everything
OL,6,FOn 20mph both Jeremy Miles and Vaughan
OL,7,FGething have pledged reviews of the
OL,8,Fpolicy introduced by the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment in September last year.
OL,11,FThe lowering of the default speed
OL,12,Flimit, which the Welsh Government says
OL,13,Fwas largely due to safety reasons, has
OL,14,Fdivided public opinion.
OL,16,FHowever, Mr Miles stuck by the policy
OL,17,Fas "the right one". He added: "It's
OL,18,Fthere to save lives and make our roads
OL,19,Fsafer but what people are telling us
OL,20,Fis they don't understand why roads
OL,21,Fthat they know are 20mph.
