OL,3,CCandidate to be next first minister
OL,4,Csays public 'profile' isn't everything
OL,6,F"So the review that I've promised will
OL,7,Fdo two things - work with councils on
OL,8,Fthe guidance but also listen to what
OL,9,Fpeople are saying to us and take that
OL,10,Finto account as we look at what roads
OL,11,Fhave been designated."
OL,13,FHe said he would not be scrapping the
OL,14,Fpolicy but would let public feedback
OL,15,F"shape" the Welsh Government's
OL,16,Fresponse to the review.
